Paul Thurston is a Canadian National Champion who has represented Canada in world competitions as player and as the captain. He gave his first lesson in the BIL on February 9 and the next is scheduled on February 23, 2012. Karen, BBO nickname (karen10) is producing a BBO movie presentation on both sessions. Make sure to attend the next session and also watch Karen's BBO movie. Here I just could not control myself and not bring you our mastery on the table that day. First I have a brief from his introduction to "Raise of a Major Suit Openings" and then let you see the three board Joyce and I played.|
